---

<section class="relative pt-32 pb-24 lg:pt-40 lg:pb-32 bg-background-dark overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 tech-grid opacity-20 pointer-events-none"></div>
  <div class="absolute inset-0 soft-gradient pointer-events-none"></div>
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-16 items-center">
      <!-- Left Column -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-7 space-y-10 text-left relative">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center space-x-3 bg-surface-dark border border-border-dark px-4 py-2 rounded-sm relative">
          <span class="flex h-2 w-2 relative">
            <span class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-primary opacity-75"></span>
            <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-primary"></span>
          </span>
          <span class="text-xs font-mono tracking-wide text-text-dim uppercase">Disponible Q4 2024</span>
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-bold text-white leading-[1.1] tracking-tight font-display relative">
          Desarrollo landings <br class="hidden lg:block" />
          estratégicas que <br />
          <span class="relative inline-block px-2 mx-1 z-10 mt-2">
            <span class="relative z-10 text-black">convierten tráfico</span>
            <span class="absolute inset-0 bg-primary -rotate-1 transform -z-10 skew-x-3"></span>
          </span>
          en clientes.
        </h1>

        <p class="text-lg text-text-dim max-w-xl leading-relaxed font-normal">
          Para coaches, marcas personales y negocios digitales que buscan escalar. Tu web no debe ser solo bonita, debe ser un <span class="text-white font-medium">activo financiero</span>.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-8 pt-6 relative items-center sm:items-start">
          <a
            class="group relative inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 border-2 border-primary bg-primary text-black text-lg font-bold shadow-none hover:shadow-brutal-white hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-200 w-full sm:w-auto"
            href="#apply"
          >
            Aplicar para proyecto
            <span class="material-icons ml-2 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform">arrow_forward</span>
          </a>
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-4 px-2 py-2 sm:py-0 relative w-full sm:w-auto">
            <div class="flex -space-x-3">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-surface-dark border border-border-dark flex items-center justify-center text-xs text-text-dim font-bold">R</div>
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-surface-dark border border-border-dark flex items-center justify-center text-xs text-text-dim font-bold">S</div>
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-surface-dark border border-border-dark flex items-center justify-center text-xs text-text-dim font-bold">M</div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col relative justify-center h-full">
              <span class="text-sm text-white font-bold flex items-center gap-1">
                Resultados Reales
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-sm">verified</span>
              </span>
              <span class="text-xs text-text-dim">En producción</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right Column (Card) -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-5 relative mt-12 lg:mt-0">
        <div class="relative bg-surface-dark border border-border-dark p-0 shadow-2xl z-10 rounded-sm overflow-hidden transform hover:scale-[1.01] transition-transform duration-500 group">
          <div class="bg-surface-dark border-b border-border-dark p-3 flex justify-between items-center">
            <div class="flex space-x-2">
              <div class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-border-dark"></div>
              <div class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-border-dark"></div>
            </div>
            <span class="font-mono text-[10px] text-text-dim uppercase tracking-wider">
              Growth_Engine_v2.0
            </span>
          </div>
          <div class="p-8 space-y-8 bg-[#0F0F0F] relative">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between relative z-10">
              <div class="flex flex-col">
                <span class="text-5xl font-bold text-white font-display">99%</span>
                <span class="text-xs text-text-dim uppercase mt-1 tracking-wider">Performance Score</span>
              </div>
              <div class="h-14 w-14 rounded-full bg-primary/5 border border-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-3xl">rocket_launch</span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="bg-background-dark p-4 rounded-sm border border-border-dark flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class="bg-green-500/10 p-1.5 rounded-sm text-green-500 mt-1">
                  <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-lg">speed</span>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <div class="text-white font-bold text-sm">Carga Instantánea = Menos Rebote y Más Ventas</div>
                  <div class="text-text-dim text-xs mt-1">Cada 100ms de retraso reduce conversiones un 7%.</div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-background-dark p-4 rounded-sm border border-border-dark flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class="bg-blue-500/10 p-1.5 rounded-sm text-blue-500 mt-1">
                  <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-lg">devices</span>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <div class="text-white font-bold text-sm">100% Responsive & Mobile First</div>
                  <div class="text-text-dim text-xs mt-1">Experiencia perfecta donde está tu tráfico.</div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-background-dark p-4 rounded-sm border border-border-dark flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class="bg-purple-500/10 p-1.5 rounded-sm text-purple-500 mt-1">
                  <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-lg">ads_click</span>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <div class="text-white font-bold text-sm">Diseño Persuasivo</div>
                  <div class="text-text-dim text-xs mt-1">Estructura enfocada en ventas, no en adornos.</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="absolute -top-6 -right-6 w-32 h-32 bg-primary/10 blur-3xl rounded-full z-0"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="torn-paper-bottom"></div>
</section>
